com.sharneng.lookup.fluent.Indexing

  • Packages that use Indexing 
    Package Description
    com.sharneng.lookup.fluent
    Contains interfaces that defined the Fluent API for building Lookup.

    • Uses of Indexing in com.sharneng.lookup.fluent

      Subinterfaces of Indexing in com.sharneng.lookup.fluent 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  Indexed<E,T extends Lookup<?>>
      Represent a indexed stage of the fluent API that enough information is collected to create a new Lookup instance, or further indexing can be added to it.
      interface  Selected<E,T>
      Represent a stage of the fluent API that the resulting member is selected for building a Lookup instance.
      interface  Sourced<E,T>
      Represent a stage of the fluent API that the source data is provided for building a Lookup instance.
